snippet.title: Monk Warriors (SMB Hack) - World 6-3
snippet.description: At the start, bounce off a spring to reach some platforms moving and collect some coins. After crossing 2 platform sets on lines, Bullet Bills will start coming. Use another spring and cross a few more platforms to reach one last mushroom tower that leads to the flagpole.
